HIGH PRIORITY (Should Have)
Feature	Why It Matters
Reaction Roles	Self-assign roles via buttons/reactions - most requested feature
Moderation Commands	/warn, /kick, /ban, /timeout, /mute - essential for mods
Level Rewards	Auto-assign roles at certain XP levels (level 5 = Member role, etc.)
Warn System	Track warnings per user with /warnings to view history
Starboard	Pin popular messages (⭐ reactions) to a showcase channel
AFK System	/afk - bot notifies when AFK user is pinged

Giveaways	/giveaway with entries, timer, winner selection
Suggestion System	Users submit ideas, community votes with ✅/❌
Invite Tracker	Track who invited who, invite leaderboard
Server Stats Channels	Auto-updating voice channels: "👥 Members: 1,234"
Birthday System	Track & announce birthdays, birthday role
Scheduled Announcements	/schedule a message for later


